@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
umount 卸载核心流程
1. 检查挂载点是否繁忙（有打开fd、进程占用）
2. 检查脏页、脏inode，全部回写磁盘
3. 释放 root inode、dentry
4. 释放 super_block
5. 从全局挂载链表移除
6. 解除挂载点绑定
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "super_block" as SB
participant "inode & pagecache" as InodeCache
participant "挂载链表" as MountList
end box
database "Disk" as Disk

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> umount("/mnt")
activate VFS

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>②</color> 查找挂载点信息
VFS -> InodeCache: <color:red>③</color> 检查是否繁忙（busy）
VFS -> InodeCache: <color:red>④</color> 同步脏数据、脏inode回写磁盘
activate InodeCache
InodeCache --> VFS: 数据全部落盘
deactivate InodeCache

VFS -> SB: <color:red>⑤</color> 释放 super_block 资源
activate SB
SB --> VFS: 超级块销毁
deactivate SB

VFS -> MountList: <color:red>⑥</color> 从内核挂载链表中移除
VFS -> VFS: <color:red>⑦</color> 解除挂载点dentry绑定

VFS --> App: <color:red>⑧</color> 卸载成功返回0
deactivate VFS
@enduml